# Hi, I'm Jenn Kunrath 👋

I am a strategic Enterprise AI Solution Engineer who sits at the intersection of complex multi-agent orchestration, rapid UI prototyping, and tangible business value. Whether I am architecting frameworks for the enterprise space or vibe-coding human-centric, value forward apps in my personal time, I treat bleeding-edge technology like my playground. 

Everything I do shares the common goal of ensuring that complex technical architectures are deeply intuitive, valuable, and above all - approachable for the user base.

---

## 🏗️ Core Frameworks & Strategic Assets

### 🔹 Decoupled Agent Frameworks (Architectural Blueprint)
I design AI infrastructure built to close the corporate "scalability gap". My core philosophy centers on creating a **reusable architecture** that can be applied across the enterprise for maximum organizational value and scale. By decoupling the foundational agent framework from the specific instruction layers, organizations can shift from building isolated, one-off solutions to deploying adaptable, scalable infrastructure. This allows teams to write and optimize a core framework once, and seamlessly repurpose it across diverse departmental use cases to accelerate digital transformation.

### 🔹 Dynamic Value Quantification Tools
I build interactive, benchmark-grounded ROI models designed to help prospective clients construct their own internal business cases in active conversations as both a scoping tool and mechanism to determine if a solution is worth building. These look across solution categories as well as logical vertical groups. Foundation is an interactive HTML/JavaScript framework mapping financial value across revenue cycle acceleration, clinical capacity recovery, and audit risk mitigation. Grounded in industry benchmarks (McKinsey and Gartner).

### 🔹 Interface Prototyping & Presales Innovation
As a founding SE, I build production-grade, front-end demos to translate abstract technical concepts into something tangible and interactive. 
*   *Featured Innovation:* Long before native agent instructions were standardized in platform interfaces, I designed and custom-built a middleware layer in client-facing web UIs to explicitly handle and visual-map multi-agent instruction routing.

---

## 💡 Personal Prototyping & Human-Centric AI

I am a massive believer in the power of **vibe coding** as an ideating tool —using natural language prompting to rapidly manifest functional software prototypes from scratch.

### 🧠 [The Mindful Journal](https://github.com/jennkunrath/mindful-journal) 
* Flagship personal project exploring the emotional utility of generative text.
* **The "Why":** Built as a deeply personal tool to offer continuous conversational support, processing text with high empathy to serve as a bridge for friends when I couldn’t physically be present for a conversation. 
* **The Tech:** Vibe-coded frontend anchored on a highly targeted, empathetic prompting schema.

### 🗺️ [Trail Tales](https://github.com/jennkunrath/trail-tales)
* A creative prototype leveraging AI to dynamically construct interactive narrative pathways encouraging kids to get involved with story building and support reading/literacy. 

