## 🎙️ Creative R&D Playground (Curiosity in Practice)

Technology is moving on a compounding acceleration curve. I stay ahead of this by actively testing, sometimes breaking, and creating with emerging tools.

*   **[JennAI.blog](https://jennai.blog):** My active sandbox for documenting enterprise AI insights, creative experiments, and technical deep-dives. It serves as a living record of my explorations, bridging the gap between high-level strategy and hands-on execution.
*   **Synthetic Voice Cloning:** Merging my decade-long background in professional voiceover with modern generative tech, I've built and mastered localized high-fidelity voice clones via ElevenLabs to explore the future of automated narration and dynamic GTM collateral. My voice clone has generated significant community engagement, surpassing **164.2k likes** in real-world validation.
*   **AI-Augmented Music Production:** Developed and produced a full pop album (Damsel) utilizing Suno to generate and master instrumental tracks, while actively deploying my traditional DAW (Digital Audio Workstation) expertise and studio vocals inside the editor to engineer a seamless harmony between human performance and algorithmic synthesis.

